 * If we divide nums into segments of size k: [nums[0..k-1]], [nums[k..2k-1]], ...,
 * and we can arbitrarily permute elements within each segment, the only way the
 * entire array can be sorted is if the multiset of elements in each original segment
 * exactly matches the multiset of elements in the corresponding segment of the sorted array.
